### 12. Log dinner
POST {{baseUrl}}/diet/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "dietPlanId": "{{planId}}",
  "date": "2025-01-15",
  "food": {
    "name": "Paneer Tikka with Salad",
    "quantity": "150g paneer, large salad",
    "mealType": "dinner",
    "time": "20:00",
    "macros": {
      "calories": 380,
      "protein": 28,
