}

### 13. Get food log for specific date
@logDate = 2025-01-15
GET {{baseUrl}}/diet/logs/user/{{userId}}/date/{{logDate}}

### 14. Get food logs for date range
@startDate = 2025-01-01
@endDate = 2025-01-31
GET {{baseUrl}}/diet/logs/user/{{userId}}/range?startDate={{startDate}}&endDate={{endDate}}

### 15. Update food log (add water intake and symptoms)
@logId = 67xyz789abc123
PUT {{baseUrl}}/diet/logs/{{logId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "waterIntake": 2500,
  "symptoms": ["slight bloating"],
  "energyLevel": 4,
  "hungerLevel": 2,
  "notes": "Felt good overall, slight bloating after lunch"
}

### ============================================
### AI RECOMMENDATIONS
### ============================================

### 16. Get AI recommendations for today
GET {{baseUrl}}/diet/logs/user/{{userId}}/recommendations

### 17. Get AI recommendations for specific date
GET {{baseUrl}}/diet/logs/user/{{userId}}/recommendations?date={{logDate}}

### ============================================
### PROGRESS TRACKING
### ============================================

### 18. Get progress for diet plan
GET {{baseUrl}}/diet/logs/user/{{userId}}/progress/{{planId}}

### ============================================
### COMPLETE WORKFLOW TEST
### ============================================

### Step 1: Create a 7-day diet plan
