### ============================================
### NOTES
### ============================================

# To use these tests:
# 1. Install REST Client extension in VS Code
# 2. Update @baseUrl if backend is on different port
# 3. Update @userId with your test user ID
# 4. Replace @planId and @logId with actual IDs from responses
# 5. Run tests sequentially for workflow, or individually as needed

# Expected Responses:
# - 200/201: Success
# - 400: Bad request (missing fields, invalid data)
# - 404: Not found (invalid IDs)
# - 500: Server error

# Tips:
# - Use "Send Request" above each ### comment
# - Check response in right panel
# - Copy IDs from responses for subsequent requests
# - Monitor backend logs for detailed error messages

